                <TD COLSPAN=2 BGCOLOR="#003399"><A name="thirdparty"><IMG SRC="/images/blue.gif" WIDTH=600 HEIGHT=3></a></TD>
        </TR>
        <TR>
                <TD VALIGN=TOP><FONT SIZE=+2>Compliance of Third Party Vendors</FONT><P>



Cabletron Systems is making every effort to procure verification of 
     Year 2000 Compliance for Third Party products resold by Cabletron.  
     This has been a difficult process and unfortunately, while some 
     Vendors offer extremely vague documentation, others have not provided 
     Cabletron with such verification.  <P>

     
     Cabletron would like to assure its customers that we will continue to 
     pursue this issue with our Third Party development partners, however 
     Cabletron cannot be held responsible for developing upgrades for these 
     products to become Year 2000 Compliant.  <P>

     
     Where available, Cabletron has provided web links to our Third Party 
     development partners' web sites offering Year 2000 Compliance 
     information.  If no information is available on the Vendor's web site, 
     and Cabletron has received written verification, Cabletron has 
     provided that verification here.  If this information is insufficient, 
     Cabletron suggests that you pursue these issues directly with the 
     vendor of the specified product.</TD>
